<title>USA: NCS Healthcare buys Cooper Hall Pharmacy.</title>
<headline>NCS Healthcare buys Cooper Hall Pharmacy.</headline>
<dateline>CLEVELAND 1997-03-04</dateline>
<text>
<p>NCS HealthCare Inc said Tuesday it acquired privately owned  Cooper Hall Pharmacy for undisclosed terms.</p>
<p>Cooper Hall is an institutional pharmacy and ancillary services provider to over 1,800 long-term care residents in South Carolina and has revenues of about $4.2 million, NCS said.</p>
